OL,6,FHarrowing mortuary crimes committed by
OL,7,Fnecrophiliac killer David Fuller, who
OL,8,Fabused at least 100 deceased women and
OL,9,Fgirls, could be repeated, an inquiry
OL,10,Fhas found.
OL,12,FThe final report of the inquiry
OL,13,Fsparked by his crimes also found that
OL,14,F"current arrangements for the
OL,15,Fregulation and oversight of the care
OL,16,Fof people after death are partial,
OL,17,Fineffective and in significant areas
OL,18,Fcompletely absent".
