OL,3,CCrimes of necrophiliac killer Fuller
OL,4,C'could be repeated', inquiry finds
OL,6,FThe maintenance worker sexually abused
OL,7,Fthe bodies of more than 100 women and
OL,8,Fgirls aged between nine and 100 while
OL,9,Femployed at the now-closed Kent and
OL,10,FSussex Hospital and the Tunbridge
OL,11,FWells Hospital, in Pembury, between
OL,12,F2005 and 2020.
OL,14,FSpeaking as the report was published
OL,15,Fon Tuesday, chairman Sir Jonathan
OL,16,FMichael said the inquiry is the first
OL,17,Ftime the "security and dignity" of
OL,18,Fpeople after death has been reviewed
OL,19,Fso comprehensively.
