OL,3,CCrimes of necrophiliac killer Fuller
OL,4,C'could be repeated', inquiry finds
OL,6,FHe said that the weaknesses that
OL,7,Fallowed Fuller to offend for so long
OL,8,Fwere not confined to Maidstone and
OL,9,FTunbridge Wells NHS Trust where the
OL,10,Fkiller worked.
OL,12,F"I have found examples in other
OL,13,Fhospital and non-hospital settings
OL,14,Facross the country.
OL,16,F"The security and dignity of people
OL,17,Fafter death, do not feature in the
OL,18,Fgovernance arrangements of many
OL,19,Forganisations which are caring for the
OL,20,Fdeceased," Sir Jonathan said.
