OL,3,CCrimes of necrophiliac killer Fuller
OL,4,C'could be repeated', inquiry finds
OL,6,FFuller was already serving a whole-
OL,7,Flife sentence for the sexually
OL,8,Fmotivated murders of Wendy Knell, 25,
OL,9,Fand Caroline Pierce, 20, in two
OL,10,Fseparate attacks in Tunbridge Wells,
OL,11,FKent, in 1987 when police uncovered
OL,12,Fhis abuse in hospital mortuaries.
OL,14,FIn November 2023 the first phase of
OL,15,Fthe inquiry, which looked at his
OL,16,Femployer Maidstone and Tunbridge Wells
OL,17,FNHS Trust, found Fuller was able to
OL,18,Foffend for 15 years without being
OL,19,Fcaught due to "serious failings" at
OL,20,Fthe hospitals where he worked.
