OL,6,FThe interim review highlighted alleged
OL,7,Fincidents including a funeral
OL,8,Fassistant taking photos of a person
OL,9,Fbeing embalmed, of people being left
OL,10,Fto decompose or covered in mouldy
OL,11,Fsheets, and the sexual assault of a
OL,12,Fdead woman by a funeral director in
OL,13,Fthe 1990s.
OL,15,FWarning that the system is
OL,16,Ffundamentally flawed, he found that
OL,17,Fdue to lack of regulation anyone could
OL,18,Fset themselves up as a funeral
OL,19,Fdirector, work at home and keep bodies
OL,20,Fin their garages if they wished.
